Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constra..._pin_endpoints(25.10)  timing_constra..._pin_endpoints(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_path_delay_include_clock_pin_endpoints

Syntax
       timing_constraint_path_delay_include_clock_pin_endpoints

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Considers  register clock pins as end-points for path delay constraints
       applied upstream.

       When set to true, the  set_max_delay  command  considers  unconstrained
       paths ending at the register clock pins.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

